thread.title: Judith
thread.title_full: Personalized Paper Manufacturing Group reviewed by Judith

author: Judith
title: Judith
text: Had never used this service before to print out pads for my dog walking business. The image I had scanned to them was inferior so they called me to see if I had another, better image. They could have just printed out the pads as is. When I received them I was very happy and will use them in the future.
